the core idea for this project is this: when are individuals in rehab improved in their odds of success by
being given opioid treatment?

Key variables to examine:
- Route of administration
- number of abuse treatment episodes
- length of stay
- age at first use
- use of other substances
- frequency of use at admission
- socioeconomic status
- age/sex/race

